dcterms:description: The Melbourne parking dataset, collected by the Melbourne City Council in 2019, contains 42,672,743 parking events recorded by the in-ground sensors every five minutes located in the Melbourne Central Business District (CBD). All sensors have been classified into 40 areas.
dcterms:title: Melbourne Parking Dataset

dcterms:description: A large-scale air quality dataset published by the Ministry of Ecology and Environment of China (MEE), comprising 92 air quality monitoring stations, to assess the hourly PM2.5 concentration in Jiangsu province in 2020.
dcterms:title: Air Quality Dataset
